gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nets 123, Spurs 103
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nets defeated the Spurs, 123-103. Cam Thomas led the Nets with 25 points and four assists as Nic Claxton (20 points, 11 rebounds, two blocks) and Dennis Schroder (15 points, 12 assists) totaled 35 points. Victor Wembanyama led the Spurs with 21 points, four rebounds, and three assists. The Nets snap a three-game skid and improve to 21-31 as the Spurs have now lost seven straight and move to 10-43.
